The paper deals with decision making and planning, which are core topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The graph model proposed by Kleinberg and Oren is related to game theory (cs.GT) and the study of incentives. The problems studied in the paper involve optimization and efficiency, which are fundamental topics in data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the computational complexity results obtained in the paper are related to complexity theory (cs.CC).
